videos.description: QB Nick Fitzgerald runs in a two-yard touchdown for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Mullen would like more consistency on offense

videos.description: Dontavian Lee finds the end zone by pushing through the defense for a three-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lee pushes the pile for TD

videos.description: Keytaon Thompson completes pass to Jamal Couch for a 11-yard  touchdown.
videos.headline: Couch TD extends the lead 45-0

videos.headline: Fitzgerald discusses the difference a year can make

videos.description: Mississippi head coach Dan Mullen happy about his team's win and gets a cup of ice poured on him in celebration.
videos.headline: Mullen enjoys 49-0 victory over Charleston Southern
